toolbar.actions.markdownDescription:
Actions of the tool, divided into 3 types as'command','replace'和'run' by "mode", e.g. 

```jsonc

"toolbar.actions": [

  {

    //动作的名称，用于引用该动作

    "name": "toggle-bold",

    "mode": "command",

    "argument": "Markdown: Toggle Bold",

    "command": "toolbar.toggle",

  }

]

```

toolbar.toolboxs.markdownDescription:
Toolboxes, e.g. 

```jsonc

"toolbar.toolboxs": [

  {

    "name": "My Box",

    "activate": true,

    "view": "mars",

    "layers": [

      {

        "name": "My Layer",

        "icon": "person",

        "tools": [

          {

            "name": "Open Extensions Folder",

            "icon": "folder-library",

            "actions": ["workbench.extensions.action.openExtensionsFolder"]

          }

        ]

      }

    ]

  }

],

```
